佔率。三星顯示器是三星電子的合併子公司。三星電子正準備把有機EL面板打造成僅次於半導體和智慧手機的主力業務，如果技術流失一事屬實，將對其經營構成嚴重打擊。"},{"pid":"111caf2bdcd1c309437f30c6ec0b96b2152f363b","tid":923938,"uid":89514,"like":28,"dislike":9,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89c340dcd955039f47a58d0f3b5bd3a8c20a29d6","tid":923938,"uid":20518,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"當初偷SONY偷唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係中國開廠預左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3f799f4f89431646f56f490cb1420dc89c53e8","tid":923938,"uid":21028,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"89c340dcd955039f47a58d0f3b5bd3a8c20a29d6","tid":923938,"uid":20518,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"當初偷SONY偷唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係中國開廠預左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:44:50.000Z","msg":"Sony 都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未唔小公司埋手偷"},{"pid":"b4aef719d3b70a66e267529586625969be891376","tid":923938,"uid":56731,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:48:05.000Z","msg":"死韓狗做得衰嘢多係時候要還啦"},{"pid":"e058c1e88e298c4765c717e8da1da845d8eccbff","tid":923938,"uid":208364,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"無人想知"},{"pid":"13935436739b314c5406d7305c5f6311c9924ff3","tid":923938,"uid":188,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"咪又係做賊起家"},{"pid":"8cd1f58ee79e6ea045a311173fcc3abda148dd93","tid":923938,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:29:52.000Z","ms